 NSAIDs should be closely monitored for hepatotoxicity.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/170356/', '', 'Rabeprazole, Misoprostol, Chondroitin sulfate, Glucosamine, Esomeprazole, Tolazoline, Rabeprazole, Dimethyl sulfoxide', 'Golimumab, Antithymocyte immunoglobulin (rabbit), Tocilizumab, Secukinumab, Canakinumab, Anifrolumab, Ravulizumab, Diroximel fumarate, Mycophenolic acid, Abatacept, Upadacitinib, More', 1767369485);
